text.section:
The Authority may:
acquire by any of the means specified in § 10-620(a) of this subtitle:
a site at Camden Yards for a facility;
a Baltimore Convention site or an interest in the site;
an Ocean City Convention site or an interest in the site;
a Montgomery County Conference site or an interest in the site; and
a Hippodrome Performing Arts site or an interest in the site; and
construct or enter into a contract to construct a facility on a site it acquires under this subsection.
